{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendBadges:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"sendBadges:","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSInteger","text":"NSInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"badge","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"badge","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current application badge number (0 to clear badge)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reports the current badge count to Pushwoosh for analytics and to enable"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"badge-based segmentation. This is useful for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analytics"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Track user engagement through unread counts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Segmentation","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Target users with high\/low badge counts","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Badge management","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Allow server-side badge manipulation"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method whenever you update the app badge to keep Pushwoosh in sync."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync badge with Pushwoosh when updating unread counts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class NotificationBadgeManager {","","    private(set) var unreadCount: Int = 0 {","        didSet {","            updateBadge()","        }","    }","","    func markAsRead(_ notificationIds: [String]) {","        unreadCount = max(0, unreadCount - notificationIds.count)","    }","","    func handleNewNotification() {","        unreadCount += 1","    }","","    func clearAll() {","        unreadCount = 0","    }","","    private func updateBadge() {","        \/\/ Update system badge","        if #available(iOS 16.0, *) {","            UNUserNotificationCenter.current().setBadgeCount(unreadCount)","        } else {","            UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = unreadCount","        }","","        \/\/ Sync with Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(unreadCount)","    }","}","","\/\/ Usage in AppDelegate","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive(_ application: UIApplication) {","        \/\/ Sync current badge state when app becomes active","        let currentBadge = application.applicationIconBadgeNumber","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(currentBadge)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/sendBadges:":{"abstract":[{"text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"sendBadges:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}